<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<title>URL Shortener</title>
		<link href='//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.1.1/css/bootstrap.min.css', rel='stylesheet')>
	</head>

<body>
	<div class="container">
		<h1>URL Shortener Microservice</h1>
		<blockquote>
		User Stories:
		<ol>
			<li>I can pass a URL as a parameter and I will receive a shortened URL in the JSON response.</li>
			<li>When I visit that shortened URL, it will direct me to my original link.</li>
		</ol></blockquote>
		<h2>Example creation usage:</h2>
		<blockquote><code>https://shurl-sp.herokuapp.com/https://www.google.com</code></blockquote>
		<h2>Example creation output</h2>
		<blockquote><pre><code>{"original_url":"https://google.com","short_url":"5933480"} Your Short URL is: https://shurl-sp.herokuapp.com/5933480</code></pre></blockquote>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
